&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Join our team&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At GoDaddy, the company that empowers entrepreneurs, our Marketing Legal team supports a range of work across growth marketing, outbound communications, performance marketing, advertising, promotions, media solutions, brand, and intellectual property. We are seeking an outstanding legal professional to contribute as a valued member of our organization!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The focus of this role will be on supporting international outbound messaging and performance marketing, including messages sent via email, short message service, voice calls, paid media, affiliate, lifecycle, web conversion funnels, advertising experiments, and new territory or new campaign assessments.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We want someone with strong legal judgment who approaches risk practically. They should learn quickly, identify patterns, and build scalable solutions. You will know when to raise novel or higher-risk issues. You will assist us in growing legal assistance for fast paced global marketing initiatives.&lt;/p&gt;
