&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist GoDaddy’s marketing teams in growing the business by delivering exceptional, risk-calibrated legal support for global campaigns, channels, offers, and customer-facing experiences&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support global outbound communications initiatives, including legal review and risk assessment for email, SMS, phone, push notifications, and other customer messaging channels across new and existing markets&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help assess legal requirements for launching outbound communications in new territories, including consent, opt-in/opt-out, disclosure, sender identification, frequency, recordkeeping, suppression, and localization requirements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support GoDaddy’s media solutions and ad tech initiatives by providing practical legal guidance on advertising products, audience targeting, measurement, campaign delivery, data use, publisher/advertiser relationships, and related commercial opportunities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Serve as a key legal partner to performance marketing teams, including support for paid search, paid social, affiliate, display, lifecycle marketing, landing pages, campaign testing, lead generation, and conversion-focused marketing initiatives&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Review marketing, advertising, promotional, social media, email, web, and customer-facing materials, including campaign copy, landing pages, creative assets, offer terms, pricing references, comparisons, claims, and disclosures&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help support promotions, sponsorships, influencer campaigns, affiliate arrangements, and

&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Location Details:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;Remote - Bulgaria&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At GoDaddy the future of work looks different for each team. Some teams work in the office full-time, others have a hybrid arrangement (they work remotely some days and in the office some days) and some work entirely remotely.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a remote position, so you’ll be working remotely from your home. You may occasionally visit a GoDaddy office to meet with your team for events or meetings.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong data-stringify-type=&quot;bold&quot;&gt;Schedule:&lt;/strong&gt; Department hours from 10:30am EEST until 1:30am EEST 7 days a week. Shifts will be within department hours which Includes weekend work. Flexibility needed to cover shifts within department hours based on business needs.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you&#39;ll get to do... &lt;/strong&gt;We&#39;re looking for a Technical Support professional to join our Investors and Enterprise Operations - Services &amp;amp; Care team. In this role, you&#39;ll support customers through clear communication, effective troubleshooting, and accurate execution of back-office tasks. You&#39;ll work in an escalated support environment where quality, empathy, and attention to detail matter.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Technical Support I is a dual role that combines customer-facing support with operational responsibilities such as transaction processing, payouts, and account verification. You&#39;ll follow established procedures while &amp;nbsp;developing deeper product knowledge and improving your technical troubleshooting skills over time.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you enjoy helping customers, solving problems, and learning new systems, this is a great opportunity to grow within a high-performing support organization.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Communicate with customers via email, phones, chat, or internal systems to understand their needs and resolve issues&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Explain technical concepts in simple, straightforward language&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide accurate updates, set expectations, and ensure a positive support experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Troubleshoot operational and technical issues using internal diagnostic tools and knowledge articles&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Escalate complex issues appropriately and document them clearly for higher-level teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Process transactions, payouts, account updates, and ID verification in line with policy&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure accuracy and compliance when handling sensitive customer and financial information&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain detailed case documentation in Salesforce and other internal tools&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Navigate Salesforce, Confluence, Slack, and diagnostic tools to complete daily work&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Participate in training, shadowing, and skill-building activities to enhance technical and operational knowledge&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong data-stringify-type=&quot;bold&quot;&gt;Your experience should include...&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fluency in English is a requirement (Written &amp;amp; spoken)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;1+ years of customer support or technical support experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong communication skills and the ability to explain technical issues in simple terms&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience using support tools such as Salesforce, Confluence, or similar platforms&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to follow structured procedures while handling a variety of customer and operational tasks&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comfort troubleshooting multi-step issues and learning new systems or technical concepts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong attention to detail and ability to work with accuracy in a fast-paced environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You might have&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledge of domains and DNS&amp;nbsp;&

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Location Details:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;United States, Remote&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At GoDaddy the future of work looks different for each team. Some teams work in the office full-time, others have a hybrid arrangement (they work remotely some days and in the office some days) and some work entirely remotely.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This position may be a hybrid or fully remote position, as decided by your manager. If designated as hybrid, you’ll divide your time between working remotely from your home and an office location, so you should live within commuting distance. If designated as remote, you’ll be working remotely from your home and may occasionally visit a GoDaddy office to meet with your team for events or meetings. Your hiring manager can share more about this role’s hybrid or remote designation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This position is not eligible to be performed in Alaska, Mississippi, North Dakota, or the Virgin Islands.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;GoDaddy is not currently considering candidates for this role in California, Seattle, or NYC.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Join Our Team&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking a Director of AI/ML to architect, define, and drive GoDaddy&#39;s three-year strategic roadmap for Generative AI and Machine Learning solutions, focused on personalized customer experiences and outcomes. This leader will deliver the latest Agentic AI and sophisticated ML techniques to craft, integrate, and scale personalized&amp;nbsp;applications globally.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you are driven by deploying AI/ML at enterprise scale, excel in showcasing innovative multi-functional system integrations, and bring experience delivering global intelligent, adaptive solutions that create exceptional value for customers and the business, we invite you to join our mission.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you&#39;ll get to do...&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strategic Vision and Roadmap: Develop and champion our ambitious vision for AI/ML applications, with clear landmarks to showcase and accelerate global customer growth&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Agentic AI Leadership: Identify and operationalize opportunities to demonstrate Agentic AI - AI agents that autonomously perceive, decide, and act, to create adaptive, intelligent systems that address evolving customer needs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;End-to-End System Integration: Own the design and implementation of detailed, robust AI/ML pipelines, ensuring reliable data ingestion, model training/deployment, and real-time application across platforms and geographies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Scalable Global Solutions and Rapid Experimentation: Architect AI/ML systems with scalability at the core while enabling rapid experimentation, iterative development, and continuous learning - ensuring consistent application performance, governance, and compliance across diverse regions and multiple customer bases&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Multi-functional Collaboration: Partner with engineering, product, data analytics, and domain teams to transform vision into deliverable products, championing methodologies for experimentation, measurement, and iteration&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Innovation and Research: Stay at the forefront of AI/ML and Agentic AI advancements, identifying new technologies and propositions to influence&amp;nbsp;our roadmap and maintain GoDaddy&#39;s competitive edge&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mentoring and Team Development: Develop, inspire, and mentor high-performing, decisive AI/ML teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Your experience should include...&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;8+ years’ validated experience in AI/ML leadership roles, in an agile Technology/SaaS business, with a portfolio of large-scale AI/ML solutions, deployed globally with deep knowledge of industry-standard ML tools, frameworks, and cloud platforms&lt;/li&gt;
