&lt;li&gt;Lead 24/7 incident management and production operations across 10+ Data &amp;amp; AI platforms, owning MTTR/MTTD targets, AAR rigor, and a root-cause-to-control loop that converts every incident into a runbook, monitoring improvement, or automation — not just a resolved ticket.&lt;/li&gt;
