&lt;p&gt;GoDaddy&#39;s Global Storage Engineering team operates one of the largest Ceph environments in the industry, powering the object, block, and file storage platforms that underpin hosting, applications, internal infrastructure, and next-generation AI/HPC workloads. If you&#39;re passionate about distributed systems, large-scale storage architecture, and solving complex reliability challenges, you&#39;ll work on infrastructure that few engineers ever experience.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
